paragraph
 Inform is a programming language and design system for interactive fiction originally created in 1993 by Graham Nelson. Inform can generate programs designed for the Z-code or Glulx virtual machines. Versions 1 through 5 were released between 1993 and 1996. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inform">Read more on Wikipedia...</a>

